[Throwback🎀 journée du 21 aout]

C’est à toi de choisir si ta beauté servira pour les valeurs de Dieu ou si elle servira à la débauche / c’est à toi de choisir si ton talent influencera positivement ou négativement.

J’ai eu à visiter il y a quelques jours l’une des galeries et maison de couture les plus prestigieuses de Paris selon l’histoire.
Ce que je retiens de bien :
•La pudeur et l’élégance des 1ère tenues 
•La passion et l’expertise avec laquelle ça a été produit 
La note un peu moins positive : ce serait sur l’une des orientations de vie de choix de l’auteur.
Toutefois,Je crois que nous sommes dans ce monde, mais nous ne sommes pas de ce monde.
À nous de discerner de prendre alors ce qui est bon, et de nous détourner de ce qui ne l’est pas.
Nb : oui j’aime bien l’art 🖼🎨👗
une belle visite que je vous recommande, notamment pour ceux qui aiment l’histoire de la France.

Welcome to the blue city of Morocco 💙🇲🇦
.
Chefchaouen is one of Morocco’s gems and one of the most unique place in the world that draws many people from around the world to visit the iconic blue streets of the blue city! 

*Couple of tips if you’d like to travel to Chefchaouen:

 #1 you gonna need maximum of 2 days to visit Chefchaouen! One day is usually enough so you can take a day trip or make a stop in Chefchaouen.

#2 There’s no airports or train stations in Chefchaouen and you can only get there by car.
If you’re visiting Tangier/ Casablanca/ Fes, you can take a bus , texi or an organized day tour to Chefchaouen and back.

#3 don’t miss visiting the Spanish mosque, shop around the Medina and take many pictures around the stunning and unique city!
 
Have fun and don’t forget to save and follow for more travel tips 💙🇲🇦✨

Well, it's that time again... #newyorkfashionweek for SP/SU24!

So we all know how great it is every time we get to see Omar Rudberg (officialomar) attend #parisfashionweek for brands like Loewe (loewe) and Valentino Beauty (valentino.beauty), and I think it would be just as great to see him #frontrow in NYC this month. And I can't think of a better brand for Omar to be invited to attend than Aknvas (aknvas) by none other than the immensely talented Christian Juul Nielsen (christianjuulnielsen)!!!

I put together a little highlight reel to show Omar's fashion #versatility and personal style. He was, after all, named Best Dressed Man by both Elle and Café magazines for a reason! At the end of this reel are some examples of the very stylish menswear line from Aknvas. Omar's slender frame and daring fashion sense are a great complement to the Aknvas #aesthetic ... it's like a match made in #fashionheaven for sure!!! Now we just need Christian and his team to agree and extend an invitation to their show. 

Ps. Christian, in the reel, I also included a photo of Wilnur (Omar's Mom) so you see where he gets both his beauty and his sense of style. You know, in case you wanted to invite her too, ☺️. I also included a photo of Omar with his costar, Wilma Lidén (wilmazparty), from his upcoming horror film Karusell (which will be showing at both the Venice and Toronto film festivals this month)... she is the female equivalent of Omar in both acting and an impeccable fashion sense. In case you wanted some fresh faces in your audience 😉. 

Can't wait to stream the show and hope to see Omar, and maybe even Wilma, there!!!

Xoxo Vanessa
